\xe2\x80\xa2 Assist GIRoA staff (AGO and MoWA) with maintaining files and online VAW statistics for clients of the VWAP.
\xe2\x80\xa2 Perform any other relevant duties as requested by the supervisor.Travels to ProvincesRequire Travels to Provinces Legal \xe2\x80\xa2 University degree in Shari\xe2\x80\x99a Law or LLB degree, LLM would be an asset.
