\xe2\x80\xa2 Identification of constraints, organizational as well as related to physical infrastructure;
\xe2\x80\xa2 Propose recommendations for improving water management practices;
\xe2\x80\xa2 Report the assessment and recommendations as part of the survey reports;
\xe2\x80\xa2 Prepare a plan of operations for water management improvements;
\xe2\x80\xa2 Water losses measurement for the selected irrigation schemes;
\xe2\x80\xa2 Discharge measurement using current meters or flow trackers and weirs;
\xe2\x80\xa2 To estimate crop water requirements;
